Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}生了个男孩  叫怀亚特·安德鲁\NBaby's a boy named Wyatt Andrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}宝宝整整11磅5盎司重\NTips the scale at a solid 11 pounds, 5 ounces.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}天哪\NGood God!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不好意思  只是...\NSorry. It's just a --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}一个大块头宝宝啊\NA huge dang kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}皮娜特要恢复可能需要一段时间了\NMight be a while before Peanut's back on her feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}祝您愉快\NYou have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}下一位\NWho's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}拜拜\NBye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}轮辋租赁区
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这个角落最合适了\NThis felt like the best corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}从路上可以看到这里\NYou know, you can see it from the road,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但是又不会遮挡什么\Nbut it's not blocking anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}过往的人应该都能吸引过来\NI figured we'd get the drive-bys and the looky-loos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:09:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们讨论的时候我态度很明确\NI was clear when we discussed this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我没有授权你使用公司资金\NI did not authorize you to use company funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我用的不是公司资金  爸  是我自己的钱\NIt's not company funds, Dad. It's my funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你哪里弄的这么多钱买这些\NWhere did you get the money to pay for all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}银行贷款\NGot a bank loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}贷款\NA loan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}用什么担保的\NSecured with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这个你不用管  爸爸\NIt's not your concern, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你用你们家房子抵押了\NYou put up your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}对\NYep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}儿子啊\NOh, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不会有事的  爸爸\NIt's gonna be okay, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我非常确定  改变是在所难免的\NI feel it in my bones. Change is inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}得走在时代前列啊\NYou got to get out in front of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.76,0:11:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}印第安泉商店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}来看还是来买\NYou a browser or a buyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}都可以\NOne of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你决定要买东西了\NWell, let me know if you decide
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}记得告诉我\Nto cross over the threshold into consumerism.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}其实我在找一件东西\NActually, I am looking for something specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:11:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我喜欢这个\NWell, I like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}有时候吧\NSometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}一个韦奇伍德炉子\NA Wedgewood Stove.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}要几个炉膛的\NHow many burners?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}四个\NFour.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}单个烤炉还有烤箱\NSingle broiler? Oven?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}下面是要带保温储物箱的还是全是烤箱的\NStorage compartment/warmer or all oven below?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}都可以\NEither, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}宽度呢\NHow wide?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}36到40英寸\N36 to 40 inches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我猜你想要好用的吧\NGood working condition, I'd imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}当然  那样最好了\NIt's preferable, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}要白色  黑色还是蓝色的\NWhite, black, blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}黑色\NBlack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}没有  根本没有韦奇伍德牌子的东西\NNope. Don't have a Wedgewood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.59,0:12:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你这里卖炉子吗\NDo you have any stoves at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.81,0:12:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不卖\NNot really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}曾经有过一大堆老古董\NUsed to keep a mess of them old-timey things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不舍得送人\NCouldn't give 'em away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}现在都留不住了\NNow you can't keep 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}都是"南方新贵族"闹的\NThe New South Bourgeoisie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你是其中一员吗\NYou part of that group?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我觉得我不够资格加入\NI don't think I qualify.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他们攒够了那些小钱\NEh, they got enough of that trickle-down money
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}就想花钱买点文化气息或品味\Nmakes 'em want to buy some culture or class or...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}或许只是淘淘旧货\Nor maybe they're just fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我也不了解  我只是尽可能的帮忙而已\NHell, I don't know. I just try to oblige when I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}所以有些小钱就归你了\NSo some of that money trickles down to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}为什么不要呢\NWell, why the hell not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我的爱国程度不亚于他们\NI'm as much of a patriot as they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我只是喜欢老式炉子而已\NI just like old stoves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}多谢你的介绍\NWell, uh, thank you for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你住在附近吗\NYou, uh, live around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是的\NI do, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我会帮你四处问问\NI'll send your request out to the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:14:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}仔细打听打听的\Nand lay my ear to the cosmic rails, as it were,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.33,0:14:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}看看有没有回应\Nwait for a reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.47,0:14:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}谢谢你\NI'd appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你觉得我在敷衍你吧\NYou think I'm bullshitting, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}正相反\NOn the contrary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这是我的电话号  过两天给我打电话\NHere's my number. Give me a call in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我会告诉你有没有线索的\NAnd I'll let you know if I got a lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}谢谢  我会打给你的\NThank you. I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}经常出门吗\NGet out much?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}什么\NI'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}比如晚上有什么社交活动吗\NYou socialize, like, at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}-天黑之后  -理论上...\N- After dark? - In theory...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}理论上  我今晚要办个派对\NWell, in theory, I'm having a party tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}地址在名片上\NMy address is on the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}要是你抗拒不了\NSo, if you're intrigued
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}狂野  奇异  精彩的东西...\Nby the wild, weird, and wonderful --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我承认  精不精彩不好说\NOkay, can't guarantee the "Wonderful."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但其他的...\NBut the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}老天爷啊\Noh, good lord god.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}总之  我很欢迎你来\NAnyway, you'd be more than welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}为什么要邀请我去你家\NWhy would you invite me to your home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}想听实话吗\NYou want me to be honest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是的\NI would, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你差不多是我见过的最孤独的人了\NYou're about the loneliest person I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}孩子  要是你来我的派对\NAnd if you come to one of my parties, son,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你可能仍感孤独  但你不会是孤身一人\Nyou may still be lonely, but you will not be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}或者喝个烂醉  看你怎么选了\NOr sober, if you so choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我叫莱斯利  名里有个Z\NName's Lezley, with a "Z."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我叫丹尼尔\NDaniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}D开头\NWith a "D."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}D开头的丹尼尔\NOkay, Daniel with a "D."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}要是我今晚没见到你\NIf I don't see you tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}或是你不想来和我们一起疯的话\Nand you don't feel like joining the fray,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,0:15:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那就过两天给我打电话问炉子的事吧\Nthen you give me a call in a few on the stove, hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}没问题\NWill do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}恕我直言  地方检察官夫人\NAll due respect, Madam district attorney,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你喝酒了吗\NHave you been drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}因为我难以想象一个神志清醒的人\N'Cause I can't imagine a sober person
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}会去考虑给丹尼尔·霍顿一个认罪协议\Neven considering offering Daniel Holden a plea deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我说过了  议员  什么都没给呢\NAnd, as I said, nothing's been offered yet, Senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但我希望你知道我很看重你的意见\NBut I did want you to know that I value your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我的意见是\NWell, my opinion is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你忘了这个案子中的事实\Nyou've forgotten the facts of this case.
