Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}求你了  妈妈\NPlease, mama,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.59,0:22:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我自己无法填补这些空白\NI can't fill in the gaps on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.32,0:22:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我需要听你讲\NI need to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.84,0:23:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那是1995年\NIt was in 1995,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.00,0:23:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}7月10号\NJuly the 10th.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.60,0:23:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我买了件新连衣裙\NI'd bought a new dress to wear...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.21,0:23:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}黄色花朵图案  那种夏季野餐经常穿的\Nyellow flowers, like a summer picnic dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.90,0:23:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那天商店快关门了我才买那件衣服的\NI-I grabbed it right before the store closed that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.48,0:23:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不知道为什么买那件衣服\NI have no idea why I bought that dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.21,0:23:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那不是我一贯风格\NIt was perverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.30,0:23:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}等离开商店的时候  我就是\NAnd when the time came to go, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.53,0:23:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我就是做不到\NI-I just couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.45,0:23:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}盖恩斯先生说这是个形式\NMr. Gaines said it was a formality,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.06,0:23:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}处决还会继续执行\Nthat the execution would be stayed again,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.99,0:23:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}可是\Nbut...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.29,0:23:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我只是一个劲儿地上下楼\NAnyway, I just kept walking up and down the stairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.83,0:23:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不停看表\Nchecking the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}最后  我来到这里看见了我的自行车\NFinally, I-I came out here. I saw my bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.55,0:23:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你爸爸听到车库门开了\NYour dad heard the garage open
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.85,0:23:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他出来问我在干什么\Nand came out and asked me what was I doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.93,0:23:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我说  我要骑车兜兜风\NI said, "I'm... I'm gonna take a ride."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.61,0:23:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}-你别去  -不  我要去\N- "No, you're not." - "Yes, I am."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.40,0:23:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}珍妮特  别逼我开车在后面跟着你\N"Janet, don't make me get in the car and follow you."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.03,0:23:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我说  就让我去吧\NI said, "Let me be."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.86,0:24:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他同意了\NAnd he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.27,0:24:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我骑着车越过整条街  穿过小镇\NRode down the street... and I rode through town,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.27,0:24:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}骑过水塔  骑过卫星站\Npast the water tower, past the satellites,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}就穿着那件可笑的黄裙子\Nin that ridiculous yellow dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.83,0:24:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我也不知道骑了多久\NI rode for I don't know how long,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.41,0:24:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}直到后半夜了我才停下\Nuntil I-I thought midnight had passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.58,0:24:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}直到停下来了  我才意识到我压到一个钉子\NWhen I stopped, I realized that I'd run over a nail
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.22,0:24:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}后轮胎都瘪了\Nand the back tire was flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.08,0:24:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我转身往回\NI turned around,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.43,0:24:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}就那样瘪着轮胎一直骑回了家\Nrode it the whole way home that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.93,0:24:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我清楚地记得当你爸爸告诉我\NI remember exactly where I was standing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.35,0:24:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他们再次延期处决你时我站在哪儿\Nwhen your dad told me that they'd given you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.95,0:24:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我就站在家门前\Nanother stay... right by the front door,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.90,0:24:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那个雕着天鹅图案的旧黄铜伞架旁边\Nby that old brass umbrella stand with the swan on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.92,0:24:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我记得是他安抚我入睡\NI remember he helped me to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.83,0:25:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我扔了那条裙子\NI threw out that dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.17,0:25:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我想我要去给自己做个三明治\NI, uh, think I'm gonna go make myself a sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.80,0:25:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你要吃一个吗\NWould you like one?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.35,0:25:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不了  谢谢\NNo, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.50,0:25:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你是哪位\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.10,0:25:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我也不知道\NI'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.24,0:25:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你看起来似曾相识\NYou look familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.25,0:26:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}如果你想起来了  能告诉我吗\NIf you figure it out, will you let me know?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.41,0:26:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}老天  我真高兴你来了\NGod, I'm glad you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.77,0:26:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}有点儿出乎我妈妈的意料\NKind of blew mom's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.47,0:26:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是因为你找的那份工作吗\NWas that the point of getting a job at...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.95,0:26:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是在哪儿来着\Nwhere, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.21,0:26:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}平价商店  乔恩\NThrifty Town, Jon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.56,0:26:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我现在在平价商店打工\NI am working at Thrifty Town
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.56,0:26:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}因为毫不夸张地说我没钱搬去亚特兰大\Nbecause I literally cannot afford to move to Atlanta,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.17,0:26:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}而梅尔文是绝不会退给我\Nand Melvin is unyielding on any refunds
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.96,0:26:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}最后一个月的房租和押金的\Nof last month's rent and deposit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.31,0:26:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他想永远把你栓在这里\NWell, he wants to keep you here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.35,0:26:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他人很好\NHe's sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.21,0:26:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他是我的情敌\NHe's my competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.52,0:26:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}事实上  生活中\NActually, the idea of having
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.86,0:26:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}出现些别的事是一种解脱\Nsomething to show up for is a relief,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.02,0:26:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}想想其他的事而不是只关注\Nto think of something other than...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.16,0:26:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你自己\Nyourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.49,0:26:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我真不敢相信你竟然这么说\NI cannot believe you just said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.55,0:26:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不过也许你说的对\NBut maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.26,0:26:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}说到工作\NSpeaking of jobs...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.30,0:27:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}威廉给我打了个很有意思的电话\NI got an interesting call from William.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.44,0:27:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}司法部门的威廉吗\NWilliam from Justice row?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.48,0:27:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他在机场给我打的电话\NHe called me at the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.36,0:27:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他说彼得·穆伦要走了\NHe said Peter Mullen's leaving
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.30,0:27:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他们要找人接替他的位置\Nand they need a replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.88,0:27:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他们是让你去吗\NAnd they're asking you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.54,0:27:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他们要我去\NThey're asking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.03,0:27:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你有多长时间考虑这件事\NHow long do you have to think about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.98,0:27:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他让我在去瓦尔纳的路上给他打电话\NHe wants me to call him on my way to Varner
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.75,0:27:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}周三还要去艾迪威尔监狱  周五是河湾监狱\Nbefore Eddyville on Wednesday and Riverbend on Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.07,0:27:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}死囚牢之旅吗\NDeath row tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.01,0:27:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们要印纪念T裇吗\NShould we print T-shirts?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.22,0:27:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我需要些改变  你明白吗\NI just need a change, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.90,0:27:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你会考虑去波士顿吗\NWould you consider Boston?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.86,0:27:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我必须现在回答你吗\NDo I have to answer right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.88,0:27:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}好好考虑下\NThink about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.19,0:27:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我会的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.87,0:27:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但是首先\NBut first,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.29,0:27:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们有一些事\Nwe have some stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.98,0:28:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}真的需要谈谈了\Nthat we really need to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.76,0:28:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}-一些事  -是啊\N- Stuff? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.60,0:28:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}超级秘密的事  而且\NIt's super-secret, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.25,0:28:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我甚至不确定\NI'm not really sure
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.09,0:28:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是否应该在这儿说\Nwe should even be out here talking about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.03,0:28:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}因为谁知道会不会有人在偷听\Nbecause we don't know who might be listening in.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.96,0:28:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}通风孔有可能安装了窃听麦克风\NMay have hidden microphones in the vents.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.31,0:28:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}麦克风\NMicrophones.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.15,0:28:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那你觉得\NDo you think it...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.04,0:28:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那你觉得如果在卧室谈会不会更安全些\Ndo you think it would be better in the bedroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.43,0:28:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}也许\NMaybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.27,0:28:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们应该检查检查\NWe should probably check.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.85,0:28:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我查这边  你去查那边\NI'll go that way. You go that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.09,0:28:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}今天把要展示的商品都布置好了\NGot the display all set up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.41,0:28:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}午饭后还有几个人来店里了\NEven had a couple folks pop in after lunch
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.84,0:28:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}来参观了一下\Nto take a look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.98,0:28:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}现在只是时间的问题了  我就知道\NOnly a matter of time now, I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.38,0:28:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}真是太好了\NThat's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.31,0:28:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}确实如此  对吗\NIt is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.15,0:29:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}真的很好\NYeah, it really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.72,0:29:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你怎么紧锁着眉头啊\NYou got the worried eyebrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.20,0:29:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}没什么\NIt's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.95,0:29:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这就意味着有问题\NWhich means it's something.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.72,0:29:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}只是因为\NWell, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.28,0:29:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我想去上学\NI want to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.61,0:29:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}上学\NSchool.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.02,0:29:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我知道有点儿突然\NI know it's kind of out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.36,0:29:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}-我只是  -什么学校\N- I just... - What kind of school?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.95,0:29:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}大学\NCollege.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.53,0:29:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我想修一些课程\NI want to take classes...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.48,0:29:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}应该是夜校课程\Nnight classes, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.45,0:29:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我还是想拿到文凭\NWant to get my degree, eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.33,0:29:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}好啊\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.03,0:29:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}好啊\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.63,0:29:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你已经考虑很久了吧\NSo, you've been thinking about this for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.89,0:29:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是有一段日子了\NA little while, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.55,0:29:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}之前怎么只字未提呢\NHow come you haven't said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.17,0:30:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.24,0:30:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}小泰  我想\NTeddy, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.65,0:30:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我的经期晚了\Nmy period's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.20,0:30:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你今天晚上真是让我各种惊喜啊\NWell, you're just full of surprises tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.65,0:30:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不是刻意如此\NI'm not trying to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.72,0:30:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你的经期之前也晚过\NYou've been late before.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.07,0:30:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.87,0:30:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但这次感觉不一样\NThis feels different.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.59,0:30:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}怎么个不一样\NDifferent how?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.90,0:30:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不知道  我想是感觉更真实吧\NI don't know. More... real, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.18,0:30:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}明白\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.31,0:30:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那么\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.08,0:30:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我是不是应该去药店买那种试纸试试\NShould I go get one of those tests from the drug store?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.43,0:30:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}应该测测吧\NI guess we should.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.84,0:30:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}好吧  现在就去买吗\NOkay. Should I go right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.82,0:30:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}等明天再去吧\NWe can wait till tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.03,0:31:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}只有我们俩吗\NJust us chickens?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.43,0:31:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}只有我们俩\NJust us chickens.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.63,0:31:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}今天早上你处理得不是很好\NYou didn't handle that well this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.73,0:31:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他是个成年人了  珍妮特\NHe's a grown man, Janet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.84,0:31:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但他受过伤害  泰德\NHe's a damaged one, Ted.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.08,0:31:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我知道  那他也不能肆意妄为\NI know that, but he can't just do things
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.70,0:31:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}然后一点责任也不负吧\Nand not face some responsibility for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.23,0:31:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我觉得他为别人的错事\NIt seems to me that he's had
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.34,0:31:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}负的责任已经够多了\Nmore than his fair share of being held responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.09,0:31:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我知道\NI realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.40,0:31:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你不知道这事对他的伤害有多大\NYou don't know how hard this is on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.09,0:31:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}大家都不好受  包括我\NIt's tough on everyone, even me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.35,0:31:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那你跟我说说你怎么不好受了\NWhy don't you tell me all about how you've suffered?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.33,0:31:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}-你没懂我的意思  -不  是你没懂\N- You're not listening. - No, you're not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.21,0:31:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不许你再像今天早上那样\NYou won't ever speak to him again the way
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.57,0:31:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}跟他说话\Nyou spoke to him this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.62,0:31:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}-我不允许  -你不允许\N- I won't allow it. - You won't allow it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.42,0:31:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这里是他的家  不能那样对待他\NHe won't be treated like that in his own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.41,0:32:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这里也是我的家啊\NWhich is my home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.63,0:32:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但他比你来的早\NIt was his first.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.15,0:32:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我去睡了\NI'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.54,0:33:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}最多是被误导了\NHe was misguided, the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.64,0:33:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我觉得你说的不对  兰诺\NI think you're wrong, Lionel.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.94,0:33:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我觉得他们是想做好事\NI think what they were trying to do is positive, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.02,0:33:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}从一开始就明显行不通\NIt was doomed from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.02,0:33:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}用哪个白痴的卡迪拉克都比这强\NOccupy some dickhead's Cadillac would have worked better.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.24,0:33:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}就像唐纳德的理想黄金国\NYeah, like the Donalds' Eldorado.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.85,0:33:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他来了  过来坐吧\NAnd this one! Chime in.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.51,0:33:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}占领运动  明确失败之处\NOccupy movement. Pinpoint its failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.64,0:33:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}占领什么\NOccupy what?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.72,0:33:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}点就在这儿\NExactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.84,0:34:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我只知道革命从来都不是\NAll I know is revolution ain't never been fomented
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.46,0:34:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那些只能住帐篷的可怜人发起的\Nby poor people sitting on their ass in tents.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.01,0:34:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}俄国革命就是农民起义来的\NThe Russian revolution was started by peasants.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.15,0:34:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}农民\NPeasants, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.54,0:34:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}虽然我不知道他们住的是不是帐篷\NI don't know if they lived in tents, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.69,0:34:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}"托尔斯泰大师"说起俄国革命\NTolstoy here talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.01,0:34:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}就好像他亲身经历过一样\Nthe Russian revolution like he was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.50,0:34:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你会想喝点的  朋友\NYou're gonna need this, friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.32,0:34:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们见过吗\NI know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.71,0:34:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}应该没有\NI don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.85,0:34:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你确定吗\NYou sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.12,0:34:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}别管他了  兰诺\NLeave him alone, Lionel.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.90,0:34:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他看起来好眼熟\NDude looks familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.06,0:34:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}派对愉快\NEnjoy your night.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.60,0:34:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}名字拼写中有D的丹尼尔来了\NYeah, that's my buddy Daniel with a "D"!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.00,0:34:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}帮我个忙  抓住那头\NGive me a hand with this thing. Grab the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.50,0:34:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}抓紧\NGrab it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.44,0:34:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这是一个老人在安斯利公园给我的\NI got it from an old queen in Ansley Park,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.06,0:34:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}怎么劝都劝不住\Nand it was not easy to talk him out of.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.35,0:34:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}进来\NRight in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.99,0:34:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}就放那  谢谢\NSet it down right there. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.56,0:34:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}绑马尾辫的怪人欺负你啦\NLittle squirrely one with a rattail giving you shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.69,0:34:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}没关系的\NIt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.40,0:35:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}哥们儿  拜托\NOh, brother, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.00,0:35:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}兰诺比你早到两个小时\NLionel gets here two hours early
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.67,0:35:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}就是为了占那把旧椅子\Njust to claim a spot on that old chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.55,0:35:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他也没什么特别的\NHe ain't got nothing else,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.85,0:35:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}除了有个两英寸的小弟弟\Nexcept a two-inch pee-pee.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.08,0:35:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我去弄杯喝的\NLet me get us a shot of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.06,0:35:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}等等\NHey, hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.91,0:35:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}站住  "逃亡列车"  你要去哪\NHold on, now, runaway train. Where you headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.48,0:35:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}回家  我\NHome. I --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.50,0:35:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那可不行  怎么能这么早就走\NNot allowed. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.48,0:35:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你不是无缘无故就来了吧\NYou came here for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.46,0:35:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}总不能空手而归\NYou best ride that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.37,0:35:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}如果我根本不知道是什么缘故呢\NWhat if I don't know the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.20,0:35:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}总会有缘由  但需要你去发现\NWell, reason's known, yet also for you to discover.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.81,0:35:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我也不知道这句话什么意思\NI don't know what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.98,0:35:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}给你  把这个系在皮带上\NBut here, hook this around your belt loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.57,0:35:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}接下来的一小时\NFor the next hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.54,0:35:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们要拴在一条绳上\Nyou and me gonna stay tethered,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.17,0:35:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}形影不离\Nremain in a radius of each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.64,0:35:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}就像围绕恒星运转的行星一样\Nlike orbiting planets.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.47,0:35:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}还是算了\NI-I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.92,0:35:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你在怕什么呢\NWhat are you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.77,0:35:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我只是不喜欢\NI'd just prefer not to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.48,0:35:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}被绑住\Ntied to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.08,0:35:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}有道理\NYou may have a point there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.10,0:35:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那就弄个隐形轨道半径吧\NOkay, we'll, uh, make the radius implied.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.39,0:36:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}-隐形的  -没错\N- Implied? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.05,0:36:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}隐形半径  不用绳子了\NImplied radius. No cord.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.60,0:36:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}就一小时  我把厨房的闹钟定好\NOne hour. I'll just set the kitchen timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.30,0:36:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这一小时里\NFor that hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.43,0:36:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这是来自伟大的\Nhere is your great mandate
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.70,0:36:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}懂的事很多的\Nfrom the mouth of the great Lezley,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.42,0:36:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}莱斯利的命令\Nwho knows not a hell of a lot --
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.56,0:36:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}假装一下\Nact as if.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.05,0:36:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}假装什么\NAs if what?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.60,0:36:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}假装属于这里  丹尼尔  跟我们一样\NAs if you belong here, Daniel, with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.32,0:36:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}跟其他乘客一样\Nyour fellow travelers.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.38,0:36:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}来吧  哥们儿  你来都来了\NCome on, buddy. You come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.88,0:36:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我想我可以喝几杯啤酒\NI suppose I could have a beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.50,0:36:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}大喊几声\NDo some yelling.
